{
  "stem": "8703.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For me, I understood, because I suffered one of them-- why the killers were Christians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This, I would like to leave to the Christians themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They should find out why the Christians were the killers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For the Jewish people, I would like to find-- they should find out why the Jewish people were the victims.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Even I didn't have a clear picture why.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Just because a son of Jewish parents, I had to become a victim.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was for many people that they couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were-- what I would like to leave-- the Jewish people should find out why they were the victims.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even the future generation should learn about it, why we suffered so much during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I lost my family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I lost my little brothers and sisters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I lost my parents, lost everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In order this shouldn't be repeated once in the histories, I would like they should study.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And see to it that the Jewish people should never, but never, be the victims of a Shoah.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we lost six million of these victims.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "During-- later on I found out that there were not just two types of people, killers and victims.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were many more people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I would say the majority of the people in Europe in the occupied by the Nazis Europe, they saw exactly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they knew exactly what happened to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They kept quiet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I call them the silent majority of the people in Europe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They didn't do a thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Just a very few people, this was the majority.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "A very minute people, maybe one in a city, two in a whole district, risked their lives, and they saved some Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "These were really something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Well these people deserve, deserve everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
